4 connected disability retirement benefit for members of
5 the Oklahoma Law Enforcement Retirement System
6 pursuant to Section 2-305 of Title 47 of the Oklahoma
7 Statutes if the members were unable to complete twenty
8 (20) years of service as a result of the disability,
9 e. which requires membership in the defined benefit plan
10 authorized by Section 901 et seq. of Title 74 of the
11 Oklahoma Statutes for persons whose first elected or
12 appointed service occurs on or after November 1, 2018,
13 if such persons had any prior service in the Oklahoma
